IF ~~ THEN BEGIN 17 // from: 2.5 5.5 7.1 13.4 14.1 15.5 23.2 24.2 25.2 26.9 27.4 28.2 29.3 31.3 32.2 33.4 34.4 35.3 36.3 37.2 114.3 115.4
